Strathgryffe 6, Newlands 3 (Strathgryffe names first): D Morrison and
Y Hutton lost to M Watt and A Christie 1-6, 6-7, 6-4; R Norris and E
Stevenson beat R Terras and S Ferguson 6-3, 6-3, 6-4; D Brown and M
Barclay beat G Reid and C Lockhart 7-6, 6-0, 1-6.
</TEXT>
