1; G Fox (West Kilbride) beat D Lucas (Worksop), 2 and 1; S Young
(Inverallochy) beat S Chapman (St Enodoc), 3 and 2; S Whiteford (Lundin)
beat P De Salvatore (Italy), 5 and 4.
Semi-finals -- Walker beat Fox, 1 hole; Young beat Whiteford, at 22nd.
