<TEXT>
* The recommended offer for Glasgow stockbroker Allied Provincial, by
Greig Middleton's parent company King &amp; Shaxson, was yesterday declared
unconditional as to acceptances.
By 3pm on Wednesday, valid acceptances had been received in respect of
93.1% of management shares and 100% of institutional holdings.
