<RECORDNO>976830533</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
MADRID: Bull-runner Jose Luis Garcia, 36, was killed yesterday at a
fiesta. Caught on the horn of the animal he was smashed against railings
and died of head injuries. Fourteen others were also hurt in the dash
through the streets.
</TEXT>
