<HEADLINE>Shark attack</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>12</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976830534</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
DAYTONA: A British holidaymaker was yesterday recovering from multiple
wounds after being bitten by a six foot shark off Florida. Mr James
Oatley, 20, of Hook, Hants, was body-boarding when the shark bit his
upper thigh. Friends managed to pull him ashore before the shark struck
again.
</TEXT>
