<RECORDNO>976830535</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
BERLIN: German TV bosses at the Sat1 station have ditched Mr Blobby
after paying Noel Edmunds #500,000 to screen his House Party series. One
BBC insider said: 'They have shown either remarkably good taste or
appalling lack of judgement, depending on your view.''
</TEXT>
