<HEADLINE>Winning ways</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>4</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976830635</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
A FOOTBALL pools syndicate yesterday won for the 57th time. The
25-strong City of London police station syndicate has been winning since
it was formed 11 years ago, its biggest success being #1,182,530 two
years ago, giving each member around #45,000. This time they received a
modest #3000.
</TEXT>
